title: Andrew Tate released from jail in Romania and placed under house arrest
description: Controversial influencer Andrew Tate and his brother have been released from jail in Romania and placed under house arrest for 30 days instead, according to court documents.

title: The King's first state visit was a post-Brexit push to sell Britain and it seems to have worked
description: You hear a lot about the soft power of the monarchy.

title: ChatGPT banned in Italy
description: ChatGPT has been banned in Italy while the country's data protection authorities investigate its collection of user information.

title: Oscar Pistorius will not be released early from 13-year jail sentence, parole board decides
description: Oscar Pistorius will not be released early from his 13-year-five-month jail sentence for killing his girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp, a parole board has decided.

title: Flo Rida's 6-year-old son in intensive care after falling from 5th floor window
description: The six-year-old son of US rapper Flo Rida is in intensive care after falling from a fifth-storey apartment window, according to legal documents filed by the boy's mother.

title: Lolita the Orca may be returned to the ocean after decades in captivity
description: An orca may return to freedom in the Pacific Northwest after more than five decades in captivity entertaining crowds in the southern US state of Florida.

title: Stressed plants emit sounds that can be heard by animals
description: Stressed plants emit sounds and these noises can be heard by animals, a new study finds.

title: Pistorious 'not remorseful or rehabilitated', Reeva Steenkamp's mother says ahead of parole hearing
description: The mother of Reeva Steenkamp has said Oscar Pistorius is "not remorseful or rehabilitated" ahead of a parole hearing that will decide if he will be freed from prison after he shot and killed his girlfriend in 2013.

title: Who is Oscar Pistorius? From 'blade runner' to convicted murderer
description: The trial of "Blade Runner" Oscar Pistorius gripped the world in 2014 when he was convicted of murdering his girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp.

title: At least 35 people killed after falling into well during celebration at temple
description: At least 35 people have died in a well after a structure built over it collapsed at a temple in central India.
